name: High Jump Kick
description: You leap into the air to deliver a strong kick to a target. Make a melee attack, doing 2d8 + MOVE fighting damage on a hit. On a miss, you take 1 damage.
higherLevels: The damage dice roll for this move changes to 2d10 at level 5, 3d10 at level 10, and 4d12 at level 17.
